	<Title>
		Coughing after quitting smoking: What&apos;s the deal?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Coughing after you quit smoking might be a sign that your body is starting to heal.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		I quit smoking six weeks ago, but now I&apos;m coughing a lot &amp;mdash; which didn&apos;t happen when I was smoking. What&apos;s going on?
	</Question>
